      "artist": "Laurence Brahm",
      "year": "2025",
      "description": "Lotus-Born Master: Journey To The Other Side Of The Black Hole – The five wisdom Dakini's consorts of Guru Padmasambhava the Lotus Born Master have come back in this era in the plot underlying this yet to be released film. By virtue of their respective cosmic powers, they have rescued our planet from the conspiracy of the imperial president and his infamous intelligence agency. Does something sound familiar... The director, through the plot of an action science fiction film, applies the teachings of Guru Padmasambhava the Lotus Born Master to the crises our present world is confronted with, and discloses the scientificity of the doctrines imparted by Guru Padmasambhava the Lotus Born Master as well as how to utilize them to convert negative energy into positive energy. \"Lotus Born Master: Journey to the Other Side of the Black Hole\" is the third part of the series of science fiction films written and directed by Laurence Brahm. The other two are \"Lotus Born Master: The Shambhala Access Code\" and \"Lotus Born Master: The Algorithm of Karma\". This series of experimental avant-garde films, has garnered more than twenty major awards at international film festivals and shocked many.",
